# No Apache Ant — ever

Do **not** introduce or recommend Apache Ant for ConceptBase.cc greenfield builds:

- **Build files**: `build.xml`, `*.ant.xml`
- **Maven plugins**: `maven-antrun-plugin`, `antrun` executions
- **Nix inputs**: `pkgs.ant`, `apacheAnt`
- **Java imports**: `org.apache.tools.ant.*`

## Use instead

| Need | Prefer |
|------|--------|
| Java libraries (JGL, Grappa, cb*) | Maven modules under `components/java/`, `components/jgl/`, `components/grappa/` |
| Legacy parent POM | `components/legacy/pom.xml` |
| Full client reactor | `cd components/java && mvn install` |
| Nix Java build | `java-reactor`, `jgl`, `grappa` derivations in `flake.nix` |

Archive snapshots under `archive/` are read-only references for sync scripts — never restore Ant
builds into `components/`. The `no-ant` flake check enforces this.
